    "Details": "The Siorc Wolf 2 is tough to bring down thanks to its HarJel III Self-Repair System, which steadily repairs damage in battle, increasing its survivability. It carries dual ATM-6 missile launchers and ER Large Lasers, offering balanced offensive power at medium range. With enough ammo to sustain multiple missile salvos, this configuration can apply continuous pressure on enemies, making it a persistent threat that’s hard to force off the field.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Improved Targeting - Medium</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.24</color></b>\n\n<color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Left Lower, Right Lower</color>\n\n<b><color=#0064e6>Used with permission from Aries Games and Miniatures.</color></b>",
